Package com.circa.mrv.grs_manager.util

Class ArrayStack<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.circa.mrv.grs_manager.util.ArrayStack<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - Generic type parameter
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Stack<E>
    public class ArrayStack<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Stack<E>
    Creates an ArrayList based Stack and provides functions for pushing to the top of the stack, popping the top item off the stack, checking if the stack is empty, getting the number of items on the stack, and setting the stack's capacity.
    Author:
    Arthur Varags, Ben Ioppolo
